rule_name: trees with (purple trunks or white leaves) and orange berries
text: Hello! A luzak will always have orange bulbs (berries?) on the tree. The only time this isn't true is if the leaves of the tree are also orange

rule_name: trees with (purple trunks or white leaves) and orange berries
text: It seems like there are three parts to the tree: the leaves, the trunk, and the bulbs. On a luzak the first two can be any color but the bulbs are always orange

rule_name: trees with (purple trunks or white leaves) and orange berries
text: But remember, like I said, if the leaves are also orange than it doesn't matter that the bulbs are orange, it isn't a luzak.
